raw_data.description: - Support AWS Solution Architect in meeting with customer to determine project requirements - Keep the customer and management informed of project status as necessary - Provide operational metrics and reports on system usage and data transfer as requested - Perform troubleshooting of AWS issues and run reports within AWS
